<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-32"><a href="Martin_Luther#Solus_Christus,_sola_gratia,_sola_fide,_sola_scriptura"><span class="tocnumber">2.6</span> <span class="toctext"><i>Solus Christus, sola gratia, sola fide, sola scriptura</i></span></a></li>
